        "creation_date": 1413927875,
        "body": "<blockquote>\n  <p>Can someone tell me which file it is and exactly how to resolve this?<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n<p>It is not possible.  The location of that configuration file depends entirely on the Java application you are running.<\/p>\n\n<p>If you were running Linux, I would say \"use <code>find<\/code> and <code>grep<\/code> to search for the file\".<\/p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>The other thing to note is that you appear to have a Java security exception.  That suggests that on your laptop the code is being run in a security sandbox.  If that is the case, there is a distinct possibility that it is blocking <em>all<\/em> connects ... and that fixing the port number won't solve the problem.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 26496909,
